<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.8.6">
<l>aṟiviṉāṟ kuṟaivillā vakalñālat tavaraṟiya</l>
<l>neṟiyellā meṭutturaitta niṟaiñāṉat torumūrtti</l>
<l>kuṟiyamā ṇuruvākik koṭuṅkōḷā ṉilaṅkoṇṭa</l>
<l>kiṟiyammāṉ kavarāta kiḷaroḷiyāṟ kuṟaivilamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except the want for [our] knowledge</l>
<l>we have no want for [our intense lustre that is not seized by mischievous Māl,</l>
<l>who took the ground by crooked taking, in the form of a short dwarf,</l>
<l>a figure of full knowledge that spoke, setting up all the paths</l>
	<l>for those of the wide world to know.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
